{"tid":2386234,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"海賊王入邊 巴基點解可以廢得咁唔合理？","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T10:37:44.000Z","uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a30d47c511b70c06107772c03efbfeb0f469f22c","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"黃道漫畫勁得唔合理好正常 特別係主角團<br />\nd主角光環 勁到有幾唔合理都可以寫得出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但巴基係反其道 廢得超唔合理<br />\n海賊王羅傑既手下 跟左羅傑幾年<br />\n最後雖然冇去到one piece <br />\n但都叫做行左大半個偉大行道<br />\n<br />\n同期紅髮做埋4皇 <br />\n雷利班死老野做曬傳說<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然走去搞左個乜鬼小醜馬戲團 海賊團<br />\n重打輸左比個乜都未識既路飛<br />\n<br />\n點解可以廢得咁唔合理<br />\n重跨張過沙鱷"},{"pid":"0a22c68fde45b6e89969c9bf6ba73a1ba9eb6aca","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"烏索普夠主角團"},{"pid":"025de523810f59e7a78ee2c3f6b4738769508938","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a22c68fde45b6e89969c9bf6ba73a1ba9eb6aca","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"烏索普夠主角團"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"勁wo 我覺得佢打得蠃巴基"},{"pid":"04c299eb3b5dfa05c49380824a7cf75dc435d51d","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"巴基9歲上羅傑船 應該起碼14，15先落船（唔肯定）<br />\n屌你老屈廢撚到 依條友依幾年搞緊咩<br />\n你話佢做船醫唔好打都講得通<br />\n但漫畫重有畫佢同紅髮一齊打敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c265688ad2dab77eb536e80dcf947b840a8e0e4","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oE8Kvgl6QT4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoE8Kvgl6QT4&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=18f80868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oE8Kvgl6QT4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個個陣重成日同白胡子海賊團開波<br />\n重要有唔錯表現 比黑胡留意到佢同紅髮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母大過左廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef1318871dd19168ff8a237a17306574ccbf6b0","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"025de523810f59e7a78ee2c3f6b4738769508938","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a22c68fde45b6e89969c9bf6ba73a1ba9eb6aca","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"烏索普夠主角團"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"勁wo 我覺得佢打得蠃巴基"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"勁過一個俾你話廢既人叫勁"},{"pid":"843de1e84af2e3bed23ff1e53e1172bacbd7b7e8","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef1318871dd19168ff8a237a17306574ccbf6b0","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"025de523810f59e7a78ee2c3f6b4738769508938","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a22c68fde45b6e89969c9bf6ba73a1ba9eb6aca","tid":2386234,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"烏索普夠主角團"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"勁wo 我覺得佢打得蠃巴基"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"勁過一個俾你話廢既人叫勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"勁過<br />\n4皇老友<br />\n羅傑船員 <br />\n重想點？"},{"pid":"f15e958ee5a4897b554e9bd5e3e46b8a56f5f09a","tid":2386234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a9582ac4f44590c3692263aee0fb1fc93a4377","tid":2386234,"uid":378926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:1